HEADWORD: Fervescent
<hw>Fer*ves"cent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>fervescens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>fervescere</ets> to become boiling
hot, incho., fr. <ets>fervere</ets>. See <er>Fervent</er>.]</ety>
<def>Growing hot.</def>⟦br⟧
